{"number":8,"verseCount":39,"verses":[[1,[["There is",["clarity-word"]]," therefore now no condemnation to them which are in Christ Jesus, who ",["walk",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Walking with God","tg/walking-with-god"],"."]]]," not after the ",["flesh",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Trust Not in the Arm of Flesh","tg/trust-not-in-the-arm-of-flesh"],"."]]],", but after the ",["Spirit",["study-note-ref","c",[["Alma 13:12 (12, 28)","bofm/alma/13.12"],"; ",["D&C 11:12 (12–13)","dc-testament/dc/11.12"],"."]]],"."]],[2,["For the law of the Spirit of life in Christ Jesus hath made me ",["free",["study-note-ref","a",[["Rom. 6:22 (11–22)","nt/rom/6.22"],"; ",["2 Cor. 3:17","nt/2-cor/3.17"],"; ",["Mosiah 5:2 (2–9)","bofm/mosiah/5.2"],". ",["TG Bondage, Spiritual","tg/bondage-spiritual"],"."]]]," from the law of sin and death."]],[3,["For what the law could not do, in that it was ",["weak",["study-note-ref","a",[["Heb. 7:18","nt/heb/7.18"],"."]]]," through the flesh, God sending his own Son in the likeness of sinful ",["flesh",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Jesus Christ, Condescension of","tg/jesus-christ-condescension-of"],"."]]],", and for sin, condemned sin in the flesh:"]],[4,["That the righteousness of the law might be fulfilled in us, who walk not after the flesh, but after the ",["Spirit",["study-note-ref","a",[["Mosiah 3:19","bofm/mosiah/3.19"],"."]]],"."]],[5,["For they that are after the flesh do ",["mind",["study-note-ref","a",["GR watch, guard."]]]," the things of the flesh; but they that are after the Spirit the things of the Spirit."]],[6,["For to be ",["carnally",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Carnal Mind","tg/carnal-mind"],"; ",["Chastity","tg/chastity"],"; ",["Man, Natural, Not Spiritually Reborn","tg/man-natural-not-spiritually-reborn"],"."]]]," minded ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," ",["death",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Death","tg/death"],"; ",["Death, Spiritual, First","tg/death-spiritual-first"],"."]]],"; but to be ",["spiritually",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Spirituality","tg/spirituality"],"."]]]," minded ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," life and ",["peace",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Peace of God","tg/peace-of-god"],"."]]],"."]],[7,["Because the ",["carnal",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Fall of Man","tg/fall-of-man"],"."]]]," mind ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," ",["enmity",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Opposition","tg/opposition"],"."]]]," against God: for it is not subject to the law of God, neither indeed can be."]],[8,["So then they that are ",["in the flesh",["study-note-ref","a",[["JST Rom. 8:8","jst/jst-rom/8.8"]," … after the flesh …"]]]," cannot please God."]],[9,[["But",["study-note-ref","a",["JST Rom. 8:9 But ye are not after the flesh, but after the Spirit …"]]]," ye are not in the flesh, but in the Spirit, if so be that the ",["Spirit",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 8:2","dc-testament/dc/8.2"],"."]]]," of God ",["dwell",["study-note-ref","c",[["1 Jn. 3:24 (19–24)","nt/1-jn/3.24"],"."]]]," in you. Now if any man have not the ",["Spirit of Christ",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Holy Ghost, Loss of","tg/holy-ghost-loss-of"],"."]]],", he is none of his."]],[10,["And if ",["Christ",["study-note-ref","a",[["2 Cor. 13:5","nt/2-cor/13.5"],"."]]]," ",["be",["clarity-word"]]," in you, ",["the",["study-note-ref","b",["JST Rom. 8:10 … though the body shall die because of sin, yet the Spirit is life, because of righteousness."]]]," body ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," dead because of sin; but the Spirit ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," life because of ",["righteousness",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Righteousness","tg/righteousness"],"."]]],"."]],[11,["But if the Spirit of him that raised up Jesus from the dead dwell in you, he that raised up Christ from the dead shall also ",["quicken",["study-note-ref","a",["GR make alive. ",["D&C 84:33","dc-testament/dc/84.33"],". ",["TG God, Power of","tg/god-power-of"],"; ",["Resurrection","tg/resurrection"],"."]]]," your ",["mortal",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Mortality","tg/mortality"],"."]]]," bodies by his Spirit that dwelleth in you."]],[12,["Therefore, brethren, we are debtors, not to the flesh, to live after the flesh."]],[13,["For if ye live after the flesh, ye ",["shall die",["study-note-ref","a",["GR are at the point of withering, dying."]]],": but if ye through the Spirit do ",["mortify",["study-note-ref","b",["GR put to death, subdue. ",["Col. 3:5","nt/col/3.5"],"."]]]," the deeds of the body, ye shall live."]],[14,["For as many as are ",["led",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Leadership","tg/leadership"],"."]]]," by the ",["Spirit",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG God, Spirit of","tg/god-spirit-of"],"."]]]," of God, they are the ",["sons",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Sons and Daughters of God","tg/sons-and-daughters-of-god"],"."]]]," of God."]],[15,["For ye have not received the spirit of ",["bondage",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Bondage, Spiritual","tg/bondage-spiritual"],"."]]]," again to fear; but ye have received the Spirit of ",["adoption",["study-note-ref","b",[["Isa. 56:3 (3–8)","ot/isa/56.3"],"."]]],", whereby we cry, Abba, Father."]],[16,["The Spirit itself beareth ",["witness",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Witness","tg/witness"],"."]]]," with our ",["spirit",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Spirit Creation","tg/spirit-creation"],"."]]],", that we are the ",["children",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Man, a Spirit Child of Heavenly Father","tg/man-a-spirit-child-of-heavenly-father"],"."]]]," of God:"]],[17,["And if children, then heirs; ",["heirs",["study-note-ref","a",[["Luke 12:44 (42–44)","nt/luke/12.44"],". ",["TG Birthright","tg/birthright"],"; ",["Election","tg/election"],"; ",["Eternal Life","tg/eternal-life"],"; ",["Exaltation","tg/exaltation"],"; ",["Man, Potential to Become like Heavenly Father","tg/man-potential-to-become-like-heavenly-father"],"."]]]," of God, and joint-heirs with Christ; if so be that we ",["suffer",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Persecution","tg/persecution"],"; ",["Suffering","tg/suffering"],"."]]]," with ",["him,",["clarity-word"]]," that we may be also glorified together."]],[18,["For I reckon that the ",["sufferings",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Adversity","tg/adversity"],"; ",["Pain","tg/pain"],"; ",["Self-Sacrifice","tg/self-sacrifice"],"."]]]," of this present time ",["are",["clarity-word"]]," not worthy ",["to be compared",["clarity-word"]]," with the ",["glory",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 58:4","dc-testament/dc/58.4"],"; ",["63:66","dc-testament/dc/63.66"],"; ",["136:31","dc-testament/dc/136.31"],"."]]]," which shall be revealed ",["in us",["study-note-ref","c",["GR to us."]]],"."]],[19,["For the ",["earnest expectation",["study-note-ref","a",["GR eager hope."]]]," of the ",["creature",["study-note-ref","b",["GR creation, material universe."]]]," waiteth for the ",["manifestation",["study-note-ref","c",["GR revelation."]]]," of the sons of God."]],[20,["For the creature was made subject to ",["vanity",["study-note-ref","a",["JST Rom. 8:20 … tribulation … ",["TG Vanity","tg/vanity"],"."]]],", not willingly, but by reason of him who hath subjected ",["the same",["clarity-word"]]," in hope,"]],[21,["Because the ",["creature",["study-note-ref","a",["GR creation, material universe."]]]," itself also shall be ",["delivered",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Deliver","tg/deliver"],"."]]]," from the bondage of ",["corruption",["study-note-ref","c",[["1 Cor. 15:42","nt/1-cor/15.42"],"."]]]," into the glorious ",["liberty",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Liberty","tg/liberty"],"."]]]," of the children of God."]],[22,["For we know that the whole creation ",["groaneth",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Earth, Curse of","tg/earth-curse-of"],"."]]]," and travaileth in pain together until now."]],[23,["And not only ",["they,",["clarity-word"]]," but ourselves also, ",["which",["study-note-ref","a",["GR who."]]]," have the ",["firstfruits",["study-note-ref","b",[["Gal. 5:22 (16–26)","nt/gal/5.22"],"."]]]," of ",["",1427],"the Spirit, even we ourselves groan within ourselves, waiting for the ",["adoption",["study-note-ref","c",[["2 Cor. 5:2","nt/2-cor/5.2"],"."]]],", ",["to wit,",["clarity-word"]]," the redemption of our body."]],[24,["For we are saved by ",["hope",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Hope","tg/hope"],"."]]],": but hope that is ",["seen",["study-note-ref","b",[["2 Cor. 4:18","nt/2-cor/4.18"],"."]]]," is not hope: for what a man seeth, why doth he yet hope for?"]],[25,["But if we hope for that we see not, ",["then",["clarity-word"]]," do we with patience wait for ",["it.",["clarity-word"]]]],[26,["Likewise the Spirit also ",["helpeth",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Holy Ghost, Gifts of","tg/holy-ghost-gifts-of"],"."]]]," our infirmities: for we know not what we should ",["pray",["study-note-ref","b",[["James 4:3","nt/james/4.3"],"; ",["D&C 46:28 (28–30)","dc-testament/dc/46.28"],"; ",["88:65 (64–65)","dc-testament/dc/88.65"],"."]]]," for as we ought: but the Spirit itself maketh ",["intercession",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Communication","tg/communication"],"."]]]," for us with ",["groanings",["study-note-ref","d",["GR sighings."]]]," which cannot be uttered."]],[27,["And he that ",["searcheth",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Judgment","tg/judgment"],"."]]]," the hearts knoweth what ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," the mind of the Spirit, because he maketh ",["intercession",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Holy Ghost, Mission of","tg/holy-ghost-mission-of"],"."]]]," for the saints according to ",["the will of",["clarity-word"]]," God."]],[28,["And we know that all things work together for ",["good",["study-note-ref","a",[["Ezra 8:22","ot/ezra/8.22"],"; ",["Alma 36:3","bofm/alma/36.3"],"; ",["D&C 90:24","dc-testament/dc/90.24"],"; ",["100:15","dc-testament/dc/100.15"],"."]]]," to them that love God, to them who are the called according to ",["his",["clarity-word"]]," purpose."]],[29,[["For",["study-note-ref","a",[["JST Rom. 8:29–30 (Appendix)","jst/jst-rom/8.29-30"],"."]]]," whom he did ",["foreknow",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG God, Foreknowledge of","tg/god-foreknowledge-of"],"; ",["Man, Antemortal Existence of","tg/man-antemortal-existence-of"],"."]]],", he also ",["did predestinate",["study-note-ref","c",["GR appointed beforehand, foreordained. ",["TG Foreordination","tg/foreordination"],"."]]]," ",["to be conformed to",["study-note-ref","d",["GR to have the same form as."]]]," the ",["image",["study-note-ref","e",[["2 Cor. 3:18","nt/2-cor/3.18"],"; ",["Col. 3:10","nt/col/3.10"],". ",["TG God, Body of, Corporeal Nature","tg/god-body-of-corporeal-nature"],"."]]]," of his Son, that he might be the ",["firstborn",["study-note-ref","f",[["TG Jesus Christ, Firstborn","tg/jesus-christ-firstborn"],"."]]]," among many brethren."]],[30,["Moreover whom he ",["did predestinate",["study-note-ref","a",["GR appointed beforehand, foreordained."]]],", them he also called: and whom he called, them he also justified: and whom he justified, them he also glorified."]],[31,["What shall we then say to these things? If God ",["be",["clarity-word"]]," for us, who ",["can ",["clarity-word"]],["be against us",["study-note-ref","a",["JST Rom. 8:31 … prevail against us?"]]],"?"]],[32,["He that spared not his own ",["Son",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Atonement through","tg/jesus-christ-atonement-through"],"."]]],", but ",["delivered",["study-note-ref","b",[["Isa. 50:8","ot/isa/50.8"],"."]]]," him up for us all, how shall he not with him also freely give us ",["all",["study-note-ref","c",[["D&C 84:38 (33–41)","dc-testament/dc/84.38"],"."]]]," things?"]],[33,["Who shall ",["lay",["study-note-ref","a",["GR accuse God’s elect."]]]," any thing to the charge of God’s elect? ",["It is",["clarity-word"]]," God that justifieth."]],[34,["Who ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," he that condemneth? ",["It is",["clarity-word"]]," Christ that died, yea rather, that is risen again, who is even at the right hand of God, who also maketh ",["intercession",["study-note-ref","a",[["Isa. 53:12","ot/isa/53.12"],"; ",["Heb. 7:25","nt/heb/7.25"],"."]]]," for us."]],[35,["Who shall separate us from the ",["l